  identifier: ReactiveEvent1
  type: 1
  question:
    sentences:
    - You are in the royal banquet. You are really bored and want to do something
      different. What will you do to liven things up?
  answers:
  - identifier: 1
    answerText: Call the alchemists to create some strange lights and smokes. What
      could go wrong?
    statChanges:
    - socialClass: 3
      changeValue: 10
    - socialClass: 4
      changeValue: 20
    - socialClass: 5
      changeValue: -10
    rivalStatChanges: []
    popChanges: []
    resolution:
      sentences:
      - '<Player> invited the alchemists to the banquet. They showed a lot of experiments
        that created funny lights and sounds. '
      - "The nobles were entertained. The Clergymen were angry because of this display
        of heresy.\r"
  - identifier: 2
    answerText: Call the castle guards to the party, they deserve it.
    statChanges:
    - socialClass: 1
      changeValue: 20
    - socialClass: 3
      changeValue: -10
    rivalStatChanges: []
    popChanges: []
    resolution:
      sentences:
      - "<Player> tought it was a good idea to invite the guards. They had a lot of
        fun and arm-wrestling contests, but the nobles didn't like the presence of
        common people in the castle.\r"
  - identifier: 3
    answerText: Give the leftovers to the commoners. It is better than to give to
      the pigs... I think.
    statChanges:
    - socialClass: 2
      changeValue: 20
    - socialClass: 3
      changeValue: -10
    rivalStatChanges: []
    popChanges: []
    resolution:
      sentences:
      - '<Player> gave the leftovers of the party to the commoners near the castle. '
      - "They were really pleased, as some of them didn't have enough to eat well
        for days. But the nobles thinks these actions aren't befitting of royalty.\r"
  - identifier: 4
    answerText: Call the pope to praise our dear Lord and give us his blessings.
    statChanges:
    - socialClass: 3
      changeValue: 10
    - socialClass: 4
      changeValue: -10
    - socialClass: 5
      changeValue: 20
    rivalStatChanges: []
    popChanges: []
    resolution:
      sentences:
      - '<Player> called the Pope to give blessings to everyone at the banquet. '
      - "The nobles liked to have a holy banquet. But the alchemists find your excess
        of faith disturbing.\r"
